dct_title_s: Imperium Turcicum in Europa, Asia et Africa regiones proprias, tributarias, clientelares sicut et omnes eusdem Beglirbegatus seu præfecturas generales exhibens
dct_description_sm: Relief shown pictorially. At head of map: Tabula ex novissimis relationibus ad mentem de I. Islii, imprimis vero celeberrimi Geographi Dni I.M. Hasii Prof. Vitemb. delineata, A. 1737. Includes ill. in title cartouche.
